entries.arrived_at_delivery: You have arrived at the drop off location. Stand by for the shuttle's arrival.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Docking completed. We are transfering the information now.
entries.docking_started_delivery: Docking procedure beginning. Please stand by.
entries.failed_destroyed: You allowed your transfer shuttle to be destroyed? That was an expensive ship. You are going to have to answer to your commander about this failure.
entries.found_loc_d: Transmitting drop off cordinates to your nav computer now.
entries.hello_d: Good to see you, pilot. We will begin docking shortly. Your superior wants to talk to you once we are done here.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with the shuttle and transfer the plans.
entries.quest_location_d: A shuttle will meet you in the Naboo system. A navigation waypoint will be sent to you once you enter that system.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Follow the supplied navigation waypoint to the shuttle's arrival location. Wait for the shuttle to arrive.
entries.title: Naboo System: Deliver the Plans
entries.title_d: Travel to the Naboo system and deliver the Rebel plans to a command shuttle that will meet you there.
